short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Terminal Mainframe is a chrome extension that gives Cytora Terminal superpowers.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
If you use Cytora Terminal, Mainframe is an extension that adds features to Terminal helpful during model debugging and customer support requests.

Terminal Mainframe: displays addressIds and LPIs for each address in a report.
